<li><a href="http://www.litencyc.com/php/speople.php?rec=true&amp;UID=5928" class="external text" title="http://www.litencyc.com/php/speople.php?rec=true&amp;UID=5928" rel="nofollow">Literary Encyclopedia</a> (in-progress)</li>
